<author>ạlạ̉b fạdy jndḥ, sẖạrl sẖlạlạ</author>
<title>wḥdk ḥbyb nfsy</title>
<lyrics>[V1]
 1- ạ̉nzlt sẖrạʿ sfynty fạlsywl jạrfh
 ryạḥ mn kl ṣwb llkẖrwf kẖạṭfh
 ṣrkẖt bnjdẗ ạlgẖryq nfsy rby kẖạỷfh
 sknt ạ̉mwạj sknyty wbklmẗ hdạ̉t ạlʿạṣfh
 2- rạ̉ytk ạtyạaⁿ mn bʿyd ʿly̱ ạlmyạẗ tmsẖy
 mqblạaⁿ knwr ạlʿyd ḍʿf ạ̹ymạny tksy
 thdyny qlbạaⁿ jdyd ʿmq kyạny tsẖfy
 ạ̉nt rby mn ạryd wḥdk ḥbyb nfsy
 3- wbʿd ạlận ln ạ̉kẖạf mn ryạḥ tjrfny
 mn sywl tsẖdny mn ạ̉mwạj tgẖmrny
 mn qywd tkblny wqḍbạn tsjnny
 fmn ạlận ạ̉nạ ḥr bạsmk tḥrrny
 4- fạ̉nt lqlby sạmʿ wbḍʿfy ʿạrf
 wbḥby tẖạbt ạ̉nt lḥyạty mkẖlṣ
 thdyny qlbạaⁿ jdyd ʿmq kyạny tsẖfy
 ạ̉nt rby mn ạ̉ryd wḥdk ḥbyb nfsy</lyrics>
</song>